"description":"SnakeRush Arcade brings the classic snake experience to modern iPhone and iPad with smooth controls, clean visuals, and fast, addictive gameplay.\n\nGuide your snake, collect food, and grow as long as possible—but don’t crash into yourself or the walls. The longer you survive, the higher your score climbs.\n\nFEATURES\n\n• Smooth swipe controls for precise movement\n• Fast-paced, responsive gameplay\n• Retro-inspired arcade design\n• Track your high score and beat your best run\n• Haptic feedback and sound effects for a satisfying experience\n• Quick restart for nonstop play\n\nPERFECT FOR QUICK SESSIONS\n\nJump in for a quick round anytime. Whether you have a minute or an hour, SnakeRush Arcade is easy to pick up and hard to put down.\n\nCHALLENGE YOURSELF\n\nEvery run is a new challenge. Improve your reflexes, plan your moves, and see how long you can survive as the speed and pressure increase.\n\nCan you master the grid and achieve the ultimate high score?\n\nDownload SnakeRush Arcade and start your run today.", "userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":0, "userRatingCount":0}, 
