"description":"Daily Brain Games is your go-to app for a quick daily mental workout. Three unique puzzles refresh every single day, keeping your mind sharp and your streaks alive.\n\nAnagram - A new word is scrambled for you every day. Tap the letters to unscramble it and solve the puzzle. Use the hint if you get stuck — but try without it first! The faster you solve it, the better.\n\nDaily Trivia - Ten hand-picked questions drawn from a pool of hundreds, covering Geography, Science, History, Math, Art, Literature, Animals, Music, Food, Sports, Technology, and General Knowledge. A fresh set every day means you'll always be learning something new.\n\nMemory Match - A 4×6 grid of face-down cards is waiting for you. Flip them over and find all 12 matching pairs. The fewer moves you make, the more stars you earn. Six different themed emoji sets rotate daily — nature, animals, fruit, music, space, and sports.\n\nFeatures:\n* Three daily games — one of each, every day\n* Puzzles reset at midnight so there's always something new tomorrow\n* Daily streak tracking for each game — build your streak and keep it going\n* Completion lock — once you've finished a game for the day, it's done. No replaying\n* Smart daily notifications at 8am — automatically cancelled if you've already played\n* Fully supports iPhone and iPad with responsive layouts\n* Works great on iOS 17 and later\n\nHow it works: Every puzzle is seeded by the date, meaning everyone around the world plays the exact same puzzles on the same day. Compare scores with friends and family — did you beat them on the trivia? Did they need fewer moves on Memory Match?\n\nDaily Brain Games is free, clean, and ad-free. No accounts, no sign-ups, no subscriptions — just open the app and play.\nA new challenge awaits you every morning. How long can you keep your streak alive?", "userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":0, "userRatingCount":0}]
